rows.label: bf08250100_0020
rows.name:
Didn't you say you wanted to destroy the world?
Kill God?

rows.label: bf08250100_0030
rows.name: I did say that.

rows.label: bf08250100_0040
rows.name: You know, I'm not so sure.

rows.label: bf08250100_0050
rows.name: What...?

rows.label: bf08250100_0060
rows.name:
I don't buy it. I can't believe that's what
you're really trying to do here.

rows.label: bf08250100_0070
rows.name:
Why do you say that?
Haven't we...

rows.label: bf08250100_0080
rows.name: I could tell when we were fighting.

rows.label: bf08250100_0090
rows.name: I saw it in your eyes. The sadness.

rows.label: bf08250100_0100
rows.name:
It was the look of someone who just wanted to die.
Someone with no other way out.

rows.label: bf08250100_0110
rows.name: [ML:undisp ](gasp)

rows.label: bf08250100_0120
rows.name:
You know...
It was the way Homura looked the first time we met.

rows.label: bf08250100_0130
rows.name: You say some interesting things. But it doesn't matter.

rows.label: bf08250100_0140
rows.name: You better believe we'll do it.

rows.label: bf08250100_0150
rows.name:
We will erase both us who were
created in this way by God,

rows.label: bf08250100_0160
rows.name: and you humans who received his blessings.

rows.label: bf08250100_0170
rows.name: We are not tools used just to keep humans alive!

rows.label: bf08250100_0180
rows.name: Well, then, there's only one thing to do.

rows.label: bf08250100_0190
rows.name: As I thought.

rows.label: bf08250100_0200
rows.name: What's that?

rows.label: bf08250100_0210
rows.name:
They're not really alive. Just autonomous cybernetic
organisms.

rows.label: bf08250100_0220
rows.name:
Once their central control is gone, they're
programmed to act on their own.

rows.label: bf08250100_0230
rows.name: To destroy.

rows.label: bf08250100_0240
rows.name: These guys?

rows.label: bf08250100_0250
rows.name:
Testaments to human hubris.
Now do you see?
